l.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/109%2c%e8%81%b2%2c2602%2c20200710%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,109,聲,2602,20200710,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"2602","JDATE":"20200710","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}